{"tid":1820272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家留意 大陸呃錢黨 雌雄大盜 up","createTime":"2020-01-11T12:24:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T12:36:02.000Z","uid":345638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e2cf07ab0361cf1422540540302a32c5cf2706","tid":1820272,"uid":345638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nLEzvKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnLEzvKM.jpg&h=948a338f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07mqCpO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07mqCpO.png&h=053d5ce7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LD6YXp3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLD6YXp3.png&h=979e0095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哩對專業呃錢黨<br />\n1月6號係紅磡出現<br />\n1月7號係將軍澳出現<br />\n1月8號係沙田大圍出現<br />\n對象：學生哥或年輕單丁人士<br />\n出沒時間：多數下午到夜晚<br />\n地點：各區 多數馬路邊<br />\n謊稱自己來自台灣，係澳門輸曬D錢，張銀行卡被櫃員機食左，身上無曬現金。周圍問人借錢吃飯搭車。又問附近有無實惠嘅旅館。當問你借到錢之後，個男嘅就會乘勝追擊再問你借多幾百。為左得到你信任，會比WeChat 同電話號碼你。但佢地用殘體字。宜家年尾，好多大陸佬落來穩食，一日呃到十個容麼易發達翻大陸過肥年😒<br />\n知道香港人對大陸人有戒心就訛稱自己係台灣人，學少少台灣腔調咁咯。<br />\n唔該大家認住佢地個樣，見到佢地即刻call popo，等佢地留係警局同popo過年。比翻D正經野popo做，費事佢地得閒無事就出去打人😒大陸呃錢黨唔撚捉，專門搞香港人。<br />\n麻煩大家share 佢地個樣開去，唔好比佢地消費香港人嘅善心。"},{"pid":"9c1c543092ac9aac39d02ef658222baaa565ba8b","tid":1820272,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=82e50b9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國議員講野無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span>"},{"pid":"5a75970160d1137607409ae34e7570b4d5758f50","tid":1820272,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"打比popo話有黑衣暴徒想呃人錢 應該5分鐘就到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c622768e77546ae1af47bae9e6a647a2869fec","tid":1820272,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"不嬲都唔幫支那人<br />\n<br />\n佢地四大國技就係偷呃拐騙"},{"pid":"bfce6ce52ef9dd491181ea610345d6ff9da62ab4","tid":1820272,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:29:17.000Z","msg":"一直都有"},{"pid":"e2dc7b388667585933bdeea1d898510b0ed15307","tid":1820272,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:34:41.000Z","msg":"屌你! 黃色經濟圈根本影響唔到d資源分配!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無所謂<br />\n因為學波蘭人將抗爭融入生活先係目的</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">明明好成功,我哋錯咗重點啫,調整心態就得</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1820242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1820242</a>"},{"pid":"35fea6bebfad9bdc8e662c7072006f22af9c4dc5","tid":1820272,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a75970160d1137607409ae34e7570b4d5758f50","tid":1820272,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"打比popo話有黑衣暴徒想呃人錢 應該5分鐘就到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"暴徒籌錢買炸藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}